original_title: Wild West 10 - Golborne Stories of Struggle and Resistance
overview: Golborne, West London, bordered by Ladbroke Grove, The Westway and the Grand Union Canal. An area that from the 1950s saw a unique struggle against poverty, greedy landlords, racism and political neglect to a musical backdrop of reggae, punk and carnival.
title: Wild West 10 - Golborne Stories of Struggle and Resistance
